tafsir[5]{c,v,t}:
  56,88,"As for if the dying person is one of those who hasten towards good..."
  56,91,"56:90"
  56,92,"And if the dying person is from the rejectors of what the Messenger (peace be upon him) brought: the deviators from the straight path..."
  56,94,"And he will have to burn in the fire of hell."
  57,1,"Every creation of His in the heavens and the earth proclaims the glory and purification of Allah. He is the almighty whom no one can overpower; the Wise in His creation and His measure."